title: GTA Online
headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Double Rewards on Air Freight Cargo Sell Missions
content:
Sell off valuable cargo in Air Freight Cargo Sell Missions this week and you’ll be rewarded with 2X the usual GTA$ and RP — stacking to a sky-high 4X for GTA+ Members.

Maximize your enterprise’s efficiency and productivity this week by recruiting Rooster McCraw’s services for sourcing Air Freight Cargo: he’s guaranteed to haul two crates in half the time.

Plus, complete 5 Resupply Missions for any business to fulfil the Weekly Challenge and bag GTA$100,000.
